                                    <LineBreak/>2. Click "START PREVIEW" to see effects in real-time
                                    <LineBreak/>3. Adjust settings while preview is running
                                    <LineBreak/>4. Click "STOP PREVIEW" when finished
                                    <LineBreak/>5. Use "REFRESH" button if buttons become unresponsive
